So okay.

1826
01:17:07,903 --> 01:17:09,370
You're right, I believe you.

1827
01:17:10,438 --> 01:17:11,572
You're God.

1828
01:17:12,973 --> 01:17:15,042
And since you're God,
you can go fuck yourself!

1829
