I didn't mean that exactly.

1830
01:17:21,314 --> 01:17:23,683
I mean, obviously I
don't want to go to hell.

1831
01:17:25,685 --> 01:17:27,153
I don't want to

1832
01:17:27,187 --> 01:17:29,456
write you off and
be tortured forever.

1833
01:17:29,489 --> 01:17:31,558
But I just, I don't
fucking get it.

1834
01:17:31,591 --> 01:17:36,596
And I'm scared, and to be
honest, I'm pissed off.

1835
01:17:37,230 --> 01:17:38,498
Yes, good.

1836
01:17:38,531 --> 01:17:40,099
Those feelings come
from the divine spark

1837
01:17:40,133 --> 01:17:41,734
that I've given you.

1838
